#![enable(implicit_some)]
// Generic MERCY sequence: spare with dialogue
// 通用 MERCY 序列：带对话的饶恕
//
// This sequence displays a spare narration using Mortar dialogue system,
// then ends the view interaction.
// The narration node is determined by the `action_param` fact (set by FRE).
//
// 此序列使用 Mortar 对话系统显示饶恕旁白，然后结束 View 交互。
// 旁白节点由 `action_param` fact 确定（由 FRE 设置）。
//
// Prerequisites / 前置条件:
//   - action_param: The Mortar node name for the spare dialogue (set by FRE)
//   - mortar_path: The Mortar file path (set by FRE)
(chapters: [
    // Run the generic narration sequence (shows dialogue, waits for completion)
    // 运行通用旁白序列（显示对话，等待完成）
    RunSequence(path: "states/battle/common/narration.sequence.ron"),

    // End the view interaction
    // 结束 View 交互
    RunSequence(path: "states/battle/common/end_view_interaction.sequence.ron"),
])
